### Submit plan to Planner
POST {{PLANNER_URL}}/plan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Summarize last meeting and email attendees"
}

### Health check - Planner
GET {{PLANNER_URL}}/health

### Direct run-task to Executor (simulate Pub/Sub push envelope)
POST {{EXECUTOR_URL}}/run-task
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": {
    "data": "{{BASE64_PLAN}}"
  }
}

### Simple direct executor call (no envelope)
POST {{EXECUTOR_URL}}/run-task
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan_id": "manual-test-1",
  "tasks": [{"id":"t1","type":"log","text":"hello from REST client"}]
}
